  <scopecontent id="aspace_9bb38188231551ae78c90060987ae95d">
    <head>Scope and Contents</head>
<p>The collection consists of twenty-four handwritten letters written in Spain. Most are from Smith to his girlfriend, identified only as "Jeanette." One is from Smith to his sister(?) Clara, and one from a friend and fellow volunteer, Harry "Jack" Boxer, to "Jeanette."  Three items are undated fragments. Several of Harold Smith's original letters are accompanied by typed transcripts.</p>  </scopecontent>
